# Atlas runtime state (SQLite DB, ledger backups, worktrees, logs, lancedb, and
# the encrypted-quarantine store) — never committed. The default config points
# these under ./.atlas/; keeping the tree out of git is what makes the quarantine
# store's "nothing ever committed" property hold for the in-repo default dir.
